{"tid":2491321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：輝瑞稱接種完兩劑疫苗後　年內或要接種第三針","createTime":"2021-04-16T08:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T08:40:30.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79d3268c137b627b1494a86e3bafaeb65ec7d4f9","tid":2491321,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"不如講下科興點先啦&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n美國輝瑞藥廠行政總裁布拉表示，在接種完兩劑新冠疫苗後的12個月內，<strong>可能還需要接種第三劑，而且可能每年都要接種加強疫苗</strong>，特別是針對變種病毒。<br />\n<br />\n他接受訪問時解釋，有如小兒麻痺症一劑已足夠的疫苗，也好像每年需重新接種的流行性感冒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n美國衛生官員亦向國會表示，應該可以預期要接種加強針，目前的構思是抵抗力較弱的人士可能會先接種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586162-20210416.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586162-20210416.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=787004be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586162-20210416.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ddfc4d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586162-20210416.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a505cea5e9b4f369381c24b3bb72cf6314f18acf","tid":2491321,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"一早預咗 話半年至一年防護力，無一隻係永久"},{"pid":"3c00131f949ee75e3250c27a818aa8ddbdf325ad","tid":2491321,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"2,3年後應該成手針窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba46616f0257aff0abb650eae89b3aee53507ee","tid":2491321,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c00131f949ee75e3250c27a818aa8ddbdf325ad","tid":2491321,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"